##### Fix `prettier-ignore` inside JSX ([#&#8203;7877](https://togithub.com/prettier/prettier/pull/7877) by [@&#8203;fisker](https://togithub.com/fisker))

<!-- prettier-ignore -->

```jsx
// Input
<div>
{
  /* prettier-ignore */
  x     ?   <Y/> : <Z/>
}
</div>;

// Prettier 2.0.2 (first output)
<div>
  {/* prettier-ignore */
  x     ?   <Y/> : <Z/>}
</div>;

// Prettier 2.0.2 (second output)
<div>{/* prettier-ignore */ x     ?   <Y/> : <Z/>}</div>;

// Prettier 2.0.3
<div>
